# Trivy CVE suppression list.
#
# One ID per line. Always pair with a comment explaining:
#   - why the finding is acceptable for this project, and
#   - when to re-evaluate (date or trigger).
#
# Audit cadence: revisit every entry on each base-image bump and
# whenever the Container Scan workflow shows a new HIGH/CRITICAL.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # <one-line justification>; review by <YYYY-MM-DD>
#
# (No active suppressions. Add entries below as findings are triaged.)
